{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Tales Beyond The Tomb&quot; is a chilling episodic horror series that plunges players into the shadows of real-life cases.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Inspired by the atmospheric horror of the 80s and 90s, each episode simulates the frightening experiences of real people, mixing nostalgia with relentless suspense.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>This is the second episode of the series:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374720/extras/gif_promote_ep2.gif?t=1734889622\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Episode 2: The Farm's Secret</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dragged into a web of secrets and lies, Samantha seems to be part of a puzzle impossible to solve. What once seemed obvious soon turns into something far more sinister, and the line between villain and victim begins to blur.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nothing is as it seems. How far will you go to uncover the truth?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Main Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>VHS Aesthetic \u2013</strong> Step back in time with visuals inspired by classic horror films from the 80s and 90s.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Photorealistic graphics and immersive environments -</strong> Feel the dread with realistic visuals and frightening scenarios.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Player voice activity -</strong> Interaction system with your microphone (no microphone is required to play, but this will increase your immersion and bring a complete experience).</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dialogue Text System \u2013</strong> Immerse yourself in the plot with dynamic, narrative dialogue.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Drive car -</strong>\u00a0Car driving system completely based on real physics.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A first-person exploration experience (walking simulator), where realism is key. Navigate immersive locations, discover disturbing truths, and face your fears.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Chef","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3374720/eafa32d4ebb7d68895819ea374625fc78de10b5d.jpg"},{"name":"Pilot","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3374720/bc8fb2c4d8744c2dba2a1a9e7263537af1151010.jpg"},{"name":"Rat","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3374720/49d6bb7a54e8ff3a5672623047129a31b62ff966.jpg"},{"name":"Landscape","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3374720/e090d3dfbfe56f140b110848ae1ebee6886837b4.jpg"},{"name":"Hidden","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3374720/9c230ed0b69468aebd7ffaa963fba3606d942c69.jpg"},{"name":"Photo","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3374720/d3fedb4da3324583b7556cde26dae38d953981bc.jpg"},{"name":"Stone Woman","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3374720/0211f849bda0f6b66e6dfa140f36975cb36ec153.jpg"},{"name":"Survivor","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3374720/db7ddbfab34540451ed47ea504d27c1b24e67f9e.jpg"}],"total":8},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374720/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734889622","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374720/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1734889622","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374720/e36927fc061e67d7